{"tid":1154372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"“新聞聯播”上熱門搜尋：談，大門敞開   打，奉陪到底","createTime":"2019-05-14T09:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T16:05:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5372bc78acfff212d1d0b9dc4700826b3ff102fc","tid":1154372,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider20190514/141/w550h1191/20190514/9323-hwzkfpt9812292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider20190514%2F141%2Fw550h1191%2F20190514%2F9323-hwzkfpt9812292.jpg&h=29913d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n情況呢，是這麼個情況：<br />\n<br />\n昨天晚上，聯播主播康輝，鏗鏘有力地念了一段&ldquo;國際銳評&rdquo;，情狀如下：<br />\n<br />\n這段評論來自總台的&ldquo;國際銳評&rdquo;，主旨意思呢如標題所言：《國際銳評丨中國已做好全面應對的準備》，其中，提到：<br />\n<br />\n對於美方發起的貿易戰，中國早就表明態度：不願打，但也不怕打，必要時不得不打。面對美國的軟硬兩手，中國也早已給出答案：談，大門敞開；打，奉陪到底。經歷了5000多年風風雨雨的中華民族，什麼樣的陣勢沒見過？ ！在實現民族復興的偉大進程中，必然會有艱難險阻甚至驚濤駭浪。美國發起的對華貿易戰，不過是中國發展進程中的一道坎兒，沒什麼大不了，中國必將堅定信心、迎難而上，化危為機，鬥出一片新天地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider20190514/141/w550h1191/20190514/dbf6-hwzkfpt9812304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider20190514%2F141%2Fw550h1191%2F20190514%2Fdbf6-hwzkfpt9812304.jpg&h=b798b41f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider20190514/141/w550h1191/20190514/f6fb-hwzkfpt9812316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider20190514%2F141%2Fw550h1191%2F20190514%2Ff6fb-hwzkfpt9812316.jpg&h=ebef24cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後的幾句話，大家之前也一定有過耳聞，重新在《聯播》這樣的平台講出來，也格外耐人尋味：<br />\n<br />\n正如習近平主席所指出，中國經濟是一片大海，而不是一個小池塘；狂風驟雨可以掀翻小池塘，但不能掀翻大海；經歷了無數次狂風驟雨，大海依舊在那兒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider20190514/141/w550h1191/20190514/25f6-hwzkfpt9812422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider20190514%2F141%2Fw550h1191%2F20190514%2F25f6-hwzkfpt9812422.jpg&h=c1e12fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這篇評論可謂典型&ldquo;三有&rdquo;，有理有力有節，其中也說到：無論外部風雲如何變幻，對中國來說，最重要的就是做好自己的事情，不斷深化改革，擴大開放，實現經濟高質量發展。美國下一步是要談，還是要打，抑或是採取別的動作，中國都已備足了政策工具箱，做好了全面應對的準備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/spider20190514/141/w550h1191/20190514/5b5f-hwzkfpt9812459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider20190514%2F141%2Fw550h1191%2F20190514%2F5b5f-hwzkfpt9812459.jpg&h=0852d6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n節目播出後，央視新聞官方微博轉發數小時，播放量和閱讀量就已雙雙突破3000萬，單條微博的點贊數量超110萬，網友留言熱烈，紛紛點贊這篇評論言之有理、&ldquo;威武&rdquo;、&ldquo;霸氣&rdquo;，同時，表示大力支持政府的反制措施，&ldquo;面對原則問題絕不低頭&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n狂風驟雨可以掀翻小池塘，但不能掀翻大海！除了點贊！還是點贊！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/2019-05-14/detail-ihvhiews1688305.d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F2019-05-14%2Fdetail-ihvhiews1688305.d.html&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=eea77ef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/2019-05-14/detail-ihvhiews1688305.d.html</a>"},{"pid":"a7e636823e3c7f837c90e98ff2751a3e11e067bd","tid":1154372,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb73d23b141a0b97ce72b9174e2ac4140ca37cd5","tid":1154372,"uid":28195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"d topic 咁撚柒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0daa58a9f01a31077fc26a1c05d8ba7c397ffabf","tid":1154372,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"即係準備食草？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/